q. What is the package name of the android app? (and hence all java files) ?

	**com.companyname.appname**
	

q. How to set title of an activity?

	Use the **setTitle** api at onCreate

	e.g: setTitle(R.string.activityTitle);

q. How to set the layout of an activity?

	Use the **setContentView** api at onCreate

	e.g: setContentView(R.layout.activity_main)

q. How to set an activity as a default activity?


	Add the below code in AndroidManifest.xml

	<activity
        android:name=".Splash"
        android:label="@string/splash_activity_title" >
        <intent-filter>
            <action android:name="android.intent.action.MAIN" />

            <category android:name="android.intent.category.LAUNCHER" />
        </intent-filter>


q. how to change the launcher logo of an app?

	In android studio, right click on app folder. New > Image asset > launcher icon.

	(or)

	change android:icon field in the AndroidManifest.xml file.(copy the image in the android:icon path. copy and change)


q. How to make the make the launcher icon circular?

	use http://romannurik.github.io/AndroidAssetStudio/ and change the icon.(or) through new image asset select circular shape
	